Package cetus.transforms

Class SingleCall

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.transforms.TransformPass
      • cetus.transforms.ProcedureTransformPass
        • cetus.transforms.SingleCall
  • public class SingleCall
extends ProcedureTransformPass
    Transforms a program such that every statement contains at most one function call. In the case of nested calls, the innermost calls will be called first. Temporaries are introduced to hold the results of function calls. Remember that this normalization does not guarantee the intended program structure (single call per statement) since there may be a case that is not normalized to provide code correctness.
